                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000402-41-off225 t18000402-41-cd226"></join>, an earthen jar, value 1d. one hundred and twenty-five penny-pieces, and nine halfpence
            </rs>, the property of 
